 fans. Finally have fun playing the game in eye-catching environments designed to immerse you in the gameplay.", "short_description": "For the first time ever, you can enjoy playing jigsaw puzzle in real 3D and in VR. Jigsaw Puzzle VR is a highly appealing game for every gender and age and a real catch for jigsaw puzzle fans. Enjoy playing 25 different puzzles from fantasy characters to cars to animals. Start a relax game with easy mode and challenge yourself all the way to hard mode created for hardcore puzzle fans. Finally have fun playing the game in eye-catching environments designed to immerse you in the gameplay."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "http://riseangle.com/games/jigsaw-puzzle-vr/jigsaw-puzzle-vr-privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "http://riseangle.com/games/jigsaw-puzzle-vr/terms-of-service", "publisher_name": "RiseAngle, Inc.", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://riseangle.com/games/jigsaw-puzzle-vr", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": null, "genres": ["ADVENTURE", "CASUAL", "EDUCATIONAL", "PUZZLE", "SIMULATION"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": null, "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["TOUCHPAD"], "supported_player_modes": [], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "648796216321020"}, "review_messages": ["", "", "", "", "This application quit unexpectedly 3/3 times on an S6 device."]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/11162683_120006955232128_1966309742632501248_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=ClIp0SYtygEQ7kNvgH6SVip&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAw2SX5YL6_v